result.execSummary:
The defendant Henry Ottoniel Lopez-Ixpata was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Henry Ottoniel Lopez-Ixpata is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Henry Ottoniel Lopez-Ixpata was found guilty of 2nd-Degree Recklessly Endangering Safety [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class G felony, Wisconsin Statutes 941.30(2).
  • Henry Ottoniel Lopez-Ixpata was found guilty of Battery [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
